3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper mentions the use of the detector in camera calibration, which is a common task in computer graphics. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing techniques for detecting chess-board features. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a new feature detector that is designed to be fast, accurate, and robust, which are important characteristics for many AI applications.
